"question":"What's the difference between archive and delete?",
"answer":"Archive is storing something out of view. All the info is still there, it's just stored in the Convo Archive, Inactive Persons Archive, Inactive Pods Archive, etc. There is no archive for Entries. You can always Unarchive an item. \r\rDelete, on the other hand, erases the item from the app, never to return. There is no Undelete.",
